quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  13,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  13,1,Alif Meeem Raa ( ae Mohammad ) yeh kitaab ( Ellahi ) ki ayatain hain. aur jo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par nazil howa hai haq hai lekin aksar log imaan nahi laatay
  13,2,khuda wohi to hai jis ne satonon ke baghair aasman jaissa ke tum dekhte ho ( itnay ) ounchay banaye. phir arsh par ja thehra aur Sooraj aur chaand ko kaam mein laga diya. har aik aik meyaad Moueen taq gardish kar raha hai. wohi ( duniya ke ) kamon ka intizam karta hai ( is terhan ) woh apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan karta hai ke tum apne perwar-digaar ke rubaroo jaane ka yaqeen karo
  13,3,aur woh wohi hai jis ne zameen ko phelaya aur is mein pahar aur darya peda kiye aur har terhan ke meoon ki do do kasmain banayen. wohi raat ko din ka libaas pehnata hai. ghhor karne walon ke liye is mein bohat si nishanain hain
  13,4,aur zameen mein kayi terhan ke qtaat hain. aik dosray se miley hue aur angoor ke baagh aur khaiti aur khajoor ke darakht. baaz ki bohat si shaakhen hoti hain aur baaz ki itni nahi hoten ( bawajood yeh ke ) pani sab ko aik hi milta hai. aur hum baaz meoon ko baaz par lazzat mein fazeelat dete hain. is mein samajhney walon ke liye bohat si nishanain hain
  13,5,agar tum ajeeb baat snni chaho to kafiroon ka yeh kehna ajeeb hai ke jab hum ( mar kar ) matti ho jayen ge tokiya az sar e no peda hon ge? yahi log hain jo apne perwar-digaar se munhkir hue hain. aur yahi hain jin ki gardnon mein taoq hon ge aur yahi ahal dozakh hain ke hamesha is mein ( jaltay ) rahen ge
  13,6,aur yeh log bhalai se pehlay tum se buraiee ke jald khawastgah yani ( taalib azaab ) hain halaank un se pehlay azaab ( waqay ) ho chukay hain aur tumhara perwar-digaar logon ko bawajood un ki be ansafyon ke maaf karne wala hai. aur be shak tumhara perwar-digaar sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  13,7,aur kafir log kehte hain ke is ( paighambar ) par is ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se koi nishani nazil nahi hui. so ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum to sirf hadaayat karne walay ho aur har aik qoum ke liye rehnuma howa karta hai
  13,8,khuda hi is bachay se waaqif hai jo aurat ke pait mein hota hai aur pait ke sukarnay aur bherne se bhi ( waaqif hai ). aur har cheez ka is ke haan aik andaza muqarrar hai
  13,9,woh danaye nihaan o aashkaar hai sab se buzurag ( aur ) aliiiii rutba hai
  13,10,koi tum mein se chupkay se baat kahe ya pukaar kar ya raat ko kahin choup jaye ya din ki roshni mein khullam khula chalay phiray ( is ke nazdeek ) barabar hai
  13,11,is ke agay aur peechay khuda ke chokidaar hain jo khuda ke hukum se is ki hifazat karte hain. khuda is ( Nemat ) ko jo kisi qoum ko ( haasil ) hai nahi badalta jab taq ke woh apni haalat ko nah badlay. aur jab khuda kisi qoum ke sath buraiee ka iradah karta hai to phir woh phir nahi sakti. aur khuda ke siwa un ka koi madadgaar nahi hota
  13,12,aur wohi to hai jo tum ko darane aur umeed dilanay ke liye bijli dekhata aur bhaari bhaari baadal peda karta hai
  13,13,aur raad aur farishtay sab is ke khauf se is ki tasbeeh o Tehmid karte rehtay hain aur wohi bijliyan bhejta hai phir jis par chahta hai gira bhi deta hai aur woh khuda ke baray mein jhagarte hain. aur woh barri qowat wala hai
  13,14,soodmand pukarna to isi ka hai aur jin ko yeh log is ke siwa pkarte hain woh un ki pukaar ko kisi terhan qubool nahi karte magar is shakhs ki terhan jo apne dono haath pani ki taraf phela day taakay ( daur hi se ) is ke munh taq aa puhanche halaank woh ( is taq kabhi bhi ) nahi aasakta aur ( isi terhan ) kafiroon ki pukaar bekar hai
  13,15,aur jitni makhloqaat asmano aur zameen mein hai khusi se ya zabardasti se khuda ke agay sajda karti hai aur un ke saaye bhi subah vsham ( sjday karte hain )
  13,16,un se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ka perwar-digaar kon hai? ( tum hi un ki taraf se ) keh do ke khuda. phir ( un se ) kaho ke tum ne khuda ko chore kar aisay logon ko kyun karsaaz banaya hai jo khud apne naffa ونقصان ka bhi ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay ( yeh bhi ) puchokiya andha aur aankhon wala barabar hain? ya andhera aur Ujala barabar ho sakta hai? bhala un logon ne jin ko khuda ka shareek muqarrarkiya hai.kiya unhon ne khuda ki si makhloqaat peda ki hai jis ke sabab un ko makhloqaat mushtaba hogayi hai. keh do ke khuda hi har cheez ka peda karne wala hai aur woh yaktaa ( aur ) zabardast hai
  13,17,isi ne aasman se meen barsaya phir is se apne apne andazay ke mutabiq naalay beh niklay phir naalay par phoola howa jhaag agaya. aur jis cheez ko zewar ya koi aur samaan bananay ke liye aag mein tapatay hain is mein bhi aisa hi jhaag hota hai. is terhan khuda haq aur baatil ki misaal bayan farmata hai. so jhaag to sookh kar zael ho jata hai. aur ( pani ) jo logon ko faida pohanchata hai woh zameen mein thehra rehta hai. is terhan khuda ( sahih aur ghalat ki ) misalein bayan farmata hai ( taakay tum samjhoo )
  13,18,jin logon ne khuda ke hukum ko quboolkiya un ki haalat bohat behtar hogi. aur jinhon ne is ko qubool nahkiya agar roye zameen ke sab khazanay un ke ikhtiyar mein hon to woh sab ke sab aur un ke sath itnay hi aur ( nijaat ke ) badlay mein sirf krdalin ( magar nijaat kahan? ) aisay logon ka hisaab bhi bura hoga. aur un ka thikana bhi dozakh hai. aur woh buri jagah hai
  13,19,bhala jo shakhs yeh jaanta hai ke jo kuch tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par nazil howa hai haq hai woh is shakhs ki terhan hai jo andha hai aur samajte to wohi hain jo aqalmand hain
  13,20,jo khuda ke ehad ko poora karte hain aur iqraar ko nahi torte
  13,21,aur jin ( rishta haae qaraabat ) ke jore rakhnay ka khuda ne hukum diya hai un ko jore rakhtay aur apne perwar-digaar se drtay rehtay aur buray hisaab se khauf rakhtay hain
  13,22,aur jo perwar-digaar ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye ( masaaib par ) sabr karte hain aur namaz parhte hain aur jo ( maal ) hum ne un ko diya hai is mein se posheeda aur zahir kharch karte hain aur neki se buraiee daur karte hain yahi log hain jin ke liye aqibat ka ghar hai
  13,23,( yani ) hamesha rehne ke baagaat jin mein woh daakhil hon ge aur un ke baap dada aur بیبیوں aur aulaad mein se jo nekokaar hon ge woh bhi ( bahisht mein jayen ge ) aur farishtay ( bahisht ke ) har aik darwazay se un ke paas ayen ge
  13,24,( aur kahin ge ) tum par rehmat ho ( yeh ) tumhari saabit qadmi ka badla hai aur aqibat ka ghar khoob ( ghar ) hai
  13,25,aur jo log khuda se ehad wasiq kar ke is ko toar daaltay aur ( rishta haae qaraabat ) ke jore rakhnay ka khuda ne hukum diya hai un ko qata kar dete hain aur malik mein fasaad karte hain. aison par laanat hai aur un ke liye ghar bhi bura hai
  13,26,khuda jis ka chahta hai rizaq farakh kar deta hai aur ( jis ka chahta hai ) tang kar deta hai. aur kafir log duniya ki zindagi par khush ho rahay hain aur duniya ki zindagi akhirat ( ke muqablay ) mein ( bohat ) thora faida hai
  13,27,aur kafir kehte hain ke is ( paighambar ) par is ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nazil nahi hui. keh do ke khuda jisay chahta hai gumraah karta hai aur jo ( is ki taraf ) rujoo hota hai is ko apni taraf ka rasta dekhata hai
  13,28,( yani ) jo log imaan laatay aur jin ke dil yaad e khuda se aaraam paate hain ( un ko ) aur sun rakho ke khuda ki yaad se dil aaraam paate hain
  13,29,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye un ke liye khushhali aur umdah thikana hai
  13,30,( jis terhan hum aur paighambar bhaijtay rahay hain ) isi terhan ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko is ummat mein jis se pehlay bohat si ummatain guzar chuki hain bheja hai taakay tum un ko woh ( kitaab ) jo hum ne tumhari taraf bhaije hai parh kar suna do aur yeh log rehman ko nahi mantay. keh do wohi to mera perwar-digaar hai is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. mein isi par bharosa rakhta hon aur isi ki taraf rujoo karta hon
  13,31,aur agar koi quran aisa hota ke is ( ki taseer ) se pahar chal parte ya zameen phatt jati ya mardon se kalaam kar saktay. ( to yahi quran un Awsaf se mutsif hota magar ) baat yeh hai ke sab baatein khuda ke ikhtiyar mein hain tokiya mominoun ko is se itminan nahi howa ke agar khuda chahta to sab logon ko hadaayat ke raste par chala deta. aur kafiroon par hamesha un ke aamaal ke badlay bulaa aati rahay gi ya un ke makanaat ke qareeb nazil hoti rahay gi yahan taq ke khuda ka wada آaa ponchay . be shak khuda wada khilaaf nahi karta
  13,32,aur tum se pehlay bhi rasoloo ke sath tamaskhur hotay rahay hain to hum ne kafiroon ko mohlat di phir pakar liya. so ( dekh lau ke ) hamara azaab kaisa tha
  13,33,tokiya jo ( khuda ) har mutnaqas ke aamaal ka nigaran ( o nighaban ) hai ( woh buton ki terhan be ilm wabay khabar ho sakta hai ) aur un logon ne khuda ke shareek muqarrar kar rakhay hain. un se kaho ke ( zara ) un ke naam to lau.kiya tum usay aisi cheeze batatay ho jis ko woh zameen mein ( kahin bhi ) maloom nahi karta ya ( mehez ) zahiri ( baatil aur jhooti ) baat ki ( taqleed karte ho ) asal yeh hai ke kafiroon ko un ke fraib khobsorat maloom hotay hain. aur woh ( hadaayat ke ) raste se rok liye gay hain. aur jisay khuda gumraah kere usay koi hadaayat karne wala nahi
  13,34,un ko duniya ki zindagi mein bhi azaab hai aur akhirat ka azaab to bohat hi sakht hai. aur un ko khuda ( ke azaab se ) koi bhi bachanay wala nahi
  13,35,jis baagh ka muttaqiyo+A1757 se wadakiya gaya hai is ke Awsaf yeh hain ke is ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain. is ke phal hamesha ( qaim rehne walay ) hain aur is ke saaye bhi. yeh un logon ka injaam hai jo mut-taqi hain. aur kafiroon ka injaam dozakh hai
  13,36,aur jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai woh is ( kitaab ) se jo tum par nazil hui hai khush hotay hain aur baaz firqay is ki baaz baatein nahi bhi mantay. keh do ke mujh ko yahi hukum howa hai ke khuda hi ki ibadat karoon aur is ke sath kisi ko shareek nah bunun. mein isi ki taraf bulaataa hon aur isi ki taraf mujhe lootna hai
  13,37,aur isi terhan hum ne is quran ko arabi zabaan ka farmaan nazilkiya hai. aur agar tum ilm ( ودانش ) anay ke baad un logon ki khawahishon ke peechay chalo ge to khuda ke samnay koi nah tumhara madadgaar hoga aur nah koi bachanay wala
  13,38,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum se pehlay bhi paighambar beje they. aur un ko bibiyanaur aulaad bhi di thi. aur kisi paighambar ke ikhtiyar ki baat nah thi ke khuda ke hukum ke baghair koi nishani laaye. har ( hukum ) qaza ( kitaab mein ) marqoom hai
  13,39,khuda jis ko chahta hai mita deta hai aur ( jis ko chahta hai ) qaim rakhta hai aur isi ke paas asal kitaab hai
  13,40,aur agar hum koi azaab jis ka un logon se wada karte hain tumhe deikhein ( yani tumahray rubaroo un par nazil karen ) ya tumhari muddat hayaat poori kar den ( yani tumahray intqaal ke baad azaab bhejen ) to tumhara kaam ( hamaray ehkaam ka ) pouncha dena hai aur hamara kaam hisaab lena hai
  13,41,kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke hum zameen ko is ke kinaroon se ghutaye chalay atay hain. aur khuda ( jaissa chahta hai ) hukum karta hai koi is ke hukum ka radd karne wala nahi. aur woh jald hisaab lainay wala hai
  13,42,jo log un se pehlay they woh bhi ( behtari ) chaalein chaltay rahay hain so chaal to sab allah hi ki hai har mutnaqas jo kuch kar raha hai woh usay jaanta hai. aur kafir jald maloom karen ge ke aqibat ka ghar ( yani injaam Mahmood ) kis ke liye hai
  13,43,aur kafir log kehte hain ke tum ( khuda ke ) rasool nahi ho. keh do ke mere aur tumahray darmain khuda aur woh shakhs jis ke paas kitaab ( aasmani ) ka ilm hai gawah kaafi hain
